replies.body:
There's nothing in the game that's pick or ban, it's all a matter of personal preference. 

Don't like snowball? Ban Vayne, Kat and Riven. Don't like solid picks that never fall off? Ban Viktor, Naut and Thresh. Don't like cheese? Ban Fizz, Jax and Cho.

@community, don't use the word "cancer" and/or other inflammatory terms if you're interested in a red response, ty.
